From: Michel Alexandre Salim <salimma@fedoraproject.org>
Date: Sun, 22 Jan 2023 14:04:40 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] Add license text
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This project is MIT licensed; the license terms require that
redistributed sources (e.g. that carried by Linux distributions) contain
a copy of the license text.

```
stats_alloc on  add-license [+]
❯ cargo package --allow-dirty --no-verify
   Packaging stats_alloc v0.1.10 (/home/michel/src/github/neoeinstein/stats_alloc)

stats_alloc on  add-license [+]
❯ tar tf target/package/stats_alloc-0.1.10.crate | grep LICENSE
stats_alloc-0.1.10/LICENSE
```

Signed-off-by: Michel Alexandre Salim <salimma@fedoraproject.org>
---
 LICENSE | 17 +++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 17 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 LICENSE

diff --git a/LICENSE b/LICENSE
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..d5075a3
--- /dev/null
